list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Fix screen recording, screenshot and media management crashes in Android 10 and above. Now live on Google Store. It works fine now with all those features working well. This version has initial features for multi-boson systems: 1) Resize screen to 8:5 aspect ratio (like that of Samsung S5E and S6...) and 2) Touch individual cam view for step-wise zoom.

task.summary: Temporary 2.0.7 app that disable screen recording so that it will not crash on Android 10. But it will still send a command to the gimmera (air) end for sd-card video recording.
